## Quality Standards

**A "good" list screen has**:
- ✅ Fast to scan (collapsed groups, clear hierarchy)
- ✅ Easy to find (search works)
- ✅ Clear actions (icon buttons)
- ✅ Helpful when empty (empty state guidance)
- ✅ Shows status (badges, indicators)
- ✅ Efficient for bulk (selection mode)

**A "great" list screen also has**:
- ✅ Delightful animations (smooth collapse/expand)
- ✅ Smart defaults (common groups expanded, rare ones collapsed)
- ✅ Contextual help (tooltips, hints)
- ✅ Keyboard shortcuts (for power users)

